/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">t_kimura</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>A \u201cBuy\u201d Rating for Shares of DRDGOLD Limited</h2> <p>This analysis gives DRDGOLD Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DRD\" title=\"DRDGOLD Limited\">DRD</a></span>) a Buy rating, reflecting an upgrade from the Hold rating given in the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703732-drdgold-has-steam-but-better-from-a-dip-drd-stock\">previous analysis</a>.</p> <p>DRDGOLD Limited, hereinafter referred to as \"DRDGOLD\", headquartered in Johannesburg, South Africa, is a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184092819/image_184092819.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743295-drdgold-profitability-is-improving-an-attractive-dip-may-not-be-far-off-rating-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 18:34:30"}, {"id": "4743322", "title": "Gold Eyes $2,700 As Fed Rate Cut Looms, Geopolitics In Focus", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold coins with hundred dollar bills\" data-id=\"142096634\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1331px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/142096634/image_142096634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1